is the Lord

00:40:40.000 --> 00:40:41.510
waiting on? He's waiting on a major

00:40:41.520 --> 00:40:43.589
harvest.

00:40:43.599 --> 00:40:45.430
I have long patience, but I'm out of

00:40:45.440 --> 00:40:47.829
time, Brennan.

00:40:50.160 --> 00:40:53.270
This

00:40:53.280 --> 00:40:55.109
dispensation of grace is coming to an

00:40:55.119 --> 00:40:56.870
end. There is a marker in the spirit

00:40:56.880 --> 00:40:59.510
realm. What are we looking for?

00:40:59.520 --> 00:41:00.950
I believe we're

00:41:00.960 --> 00:41:02.309
about to see one of the greatest

00:41:02.309 --> 00:41:02.319
harvests

00:41:02.319 --> 00:41:04.309
of souls this world has ever seen.

00:41:04.319 --> 00:41:07.030
As he signs things and the Pope

00:41:07.040 --> 00:41:09.030
signs this, signs the book, and does

00:41:09.040 --> 00:41:10.069
all these things, and they're all hanging

00:41:10.079 --> 00:41:15.190
out together, what are we about to see?

00:41:15.200 --> 00:41:17.589
Where are we at

00:41:17.599 --> 00:41:20.150
in all that we see all around

00:41:20.160 --> 00:41:22.470
us? Look what's happening with the war

00:41:22.480 --> 00:41:25.670
and all this stuff. Right. Interesting.

00:41:25.680 --> 00:41:27.109
So, all right. You want to read any of

00:41:27.119 --> 00:41:29.589
this? It kind of changed the atmosphere.

00:41:29.599 --> 00:41:30.470
Okay.

00:41:31.920 --> 00:41:34.069
I feel like we did okay

00:41:34.079 --> 00:41:35.670
here with that. I brought everything

00:41:35.680 --> 00:41:36.390
out, right?

00:41:36.400 --> 00:41:36.950
Yes.

00:41:36.960 --> 00:41:39.109
Okay. It's good of what we see today in

00:41:39.119 --> 00:41:40.630
the news.

00:41:40.640 --> 00:41:41.990
Anything else from Trump or anything?

00:41:42.000 --> 00:41:43.109
You don't want to say nothing? What is

00:41:43.119 --> 00:41:44.150
he doing today?

00:41:44.160 --> 00:41:46.069
He said that he walked

00:41:46.079 --> 00:41:48.230
the Strait and then China

00:41:48.240 --> 00:41:50.550
says blockade is dangerous and

00:41:50.560 --> 00:41:55.109
irresponsible,

00:41:55.119 --> 00:42:01.030
right?

00:42:01.040 --> 00:42:06.150
So, all right.

00:42:06.160 --> 00:42:08.470
Greed. It's good. I like it when you

00:42:08.480 --> 00:42:10.150
read to me.

00:42:34.720 --> 00:42:37.030
I've seen it: meetings full of hype,

00:42:37.040 --> 00:42:39.270
noise, even passion, but the altar

00:42:39.280 --> 00:42:41.349
remains untouched. Why? Because the

00:42:41.359 --> 00:42:43.430
ground wasn't broken in prayer. You

00:42:43.440 --> 00:42:46.069
can't reap where no one has plowed. The

00:42:46.079 --> 00:42:48.390
altar is not a magic space; it's a

00:42:48.400 --> 00:42:50.230
manifestation of what's already been

00:42:50.240 --> 00:42:53.670
birthed in intercession. Empty altars

00:42:53.680 --> 00:42:58.790
reveal empty prayer closets.

00:42:58.800 --> 00:43:00.950
The tears in secret become fire in

00:43:00.960 --> 00:43:02.870
public. The altars that overflowed

00:43:02.880 --> 00:43:04.710
during Finney's meetings weren't the

00:43:04.720 --> 00:43:06.309
result of his gift. They were the

00:43:06.319 --> 00:43:08.790
result of my tears. I cried in secret

00:43:08.800 --> 00:43:11.510
until the ground groaned for salvation.

00:43:11.520 --> 00:43:13.750
If you want to see weeping at the altar,

00:43:13.760 --> 00:43:17.030
you must first weep on the floor. Heaven

00:43:17.040 --> 00:43:20.470
answers seeded ground. No intercession,

00:43:20.480 --> 00:43:22.390
no harvest.

00:43:22.400 --> 00:43:24.470
Don't blame the people. Blame the

00:43:24.480 --> 00:43:26.230
preparation. Too many blame the

00:43:26.240 --> 00:43:28.150
congregation when revival doesn't fall.

00:43:28.160 --> 00:43:31.910
But I ask: who prayed? Who fasted? Who

00:43:31.920 --> 00:43:34.550
groaned? Who interceded with travail

00:43:34.560 --> 00:43:36.230
until the Spirit hovered over the

00:43:36.240 --> 00:43:38.550
gathering? Altars don't fall by

00:43:38.560 --> 00:43:40.710
accident. They fill when intercessors

00:43:40.720 --> 00:43:46.550
dig deep wells in prayer.

00:43:46.560 --> 00:43:48.470
How to fill the altars with heaven's

00:43:48.480 --> 00:43:50.950
glory: break up the ground in prayer.

00:43:50.960 --> 00:43:52.870
Tear down resistance before the people

00:43:52.880 --> 00:43:55.190
arrive. Saturate the meeting. Pray over

00:43:55.200 --> 00:43:57.589
every seat, every soul, every moment.

00:43:57.599 --> 00:43:59.829
Invite holy conviction. Ask the Spirit

00:43:59.839 --> 00:44:02.069
to rest heavy before the first note is

00:44:02.079 --> 00:44:04.870
sung.

00:44:04.880 --> 00:44:06.790
'Holy Spirit, let no altar be empty

00:44:06.800 --> 00:44:09.109
because I failed to pray. Use my tears

00:44:09.119 --> 00:44:11.589
to water the soil of revival. Let my

00:44:11.599 --> 00:44:13.510
intercession prepare the way for souls

00:44:13.520 --> 00:44:15.109
to come running. Break the ground

00:44:15.119 --> 00:44:17.030
through me. Shake the atmosphere through

00:44:17.040 --> 00:44:19.190
me. Let altars burn with conviction,

00:44:19.200 --> 00:44:21.589
glory, and

00:44:21.589 --> 00:44:21.599
transformation.'The

00:44:21.599 --> 00:44:23.990
true intercessor—this is

00:44:23.990 --> 00:44:24.000
the watchman

00:44:24.000 --> 00:44:26.150
who never leaves their post. The

00:44:26.160 --> 00:44:28.950
true intercessor is always on guard. You

00:44:28.960 --> 00:44:30.710
don't clock out when you carry

00:44:30.720 --> 00:44:33.190
heaven's burden. You don't pray once and

00:44:33.200 --> 00:44:35.589
walk away. You stay on the wall. You

00:44:35.599 --> 00:44:39.109
watch, you wait, you discern, you press.

00:44:39.119 --> 00:44:41.750
I was a watchman and I never left my

00:44:41.760 --> 00:44:44.710
post. Even when the meetings were done,

00:44:44.720 --> 00:44:47.589
I stayed because I knew the war wasn't

00:44:47.599 --> 00:44:49.910
over; it was only beginning.

00:44:49.920 --> 00:44:51.990
Intercession isn't a moment; it's a

00:44:52.000 --> 00:44:55.510
mantle. You must monitor the spiritual

00:44:55.520 --> 00:44:57.750
atmosphere. There were nights when I

00:44:57.760 --> 00:45:00.309
felt the atmosphere shift mid-revival.

00:45:00.319 --> 00:45:03.030
Complacency tried to creep in, demonic

00:45:03.030 --> 00:45:03.040
pushback

00:45:03.040 --> 00:45:05.430
surged, and I knew I

00:45:05.430 --> 00:45:05.440
couldn't

00:45:05.440 --> 00:45:07.750
leave my watch. I had to

00:45:07.760 --> 00:45:10.870
war again, fast again, groan again. Just

00:45:10.880 --> 00:45:13.190
because revival starts

00:45:13.200 --> 00:45:15.750
doesn't mean it continues. Watchmen

00:45:15.760 --> 00:45:18.150
sustain what

00:45:18.160 --> 00:45:20.870
others initiate. God is looking for

00:45:20.880 --> 00:45:24.150
watchmen in this generation. The wall is

00:45:24.160 --> 00:45:27.589
too empty, the gaps are too wide. The

00:45:27.599 --> 00:45:30.069
pulpits are full, but the prayer closets

00:45:30.079 --> 00:45:31.910
are abandoned.

00:45:31.920 --> 00:45:34.470
The church needs watchmen, intercessors

00:45:34.480 --> 00:45:36.870
who don't just pray once, but who own

00:45:36.880 --> 00:45:39.990
the ground with persistence. Be the one

00:45:40.000 --> 00:45:52.390
who never leaves your post.

00:45:52.400 --> 00:45:55.270
True intercession is often lonely. No

00:45:55.280 --> 00:45:57.750
crowd, no applause, no social media

00:45:57.760 --> 00:45:59.750
updates. Just you, the carpet, and the

00:45:59.760 --> 00:46:01.990
groan. I lived it. Most of my

00:46:02.000 --> 00:46:04.550
breakthroughs were birthed alone,

00:46:04.560 --> 00:46:06.950
because revival begins in isolation

00:46:06.960 --> 00:46:09.430
before it ever reaches the masses. God

00:46:09.440 --> 00:46:11.910
doesn't need a crowd to start a move; He

00:46:11.920 --> 00:46:13.670
just needs one willing voice in the

00:46:13.680 --> 00:46:15.829
wilderness. Are you willing to be that

00:46:15.839 --> 00:46:17.670
one?

00:46:17.680 --> 00:46:20.150
Don't resent the loneliness. Heaven

00:46:20.160 --> 00:46:22.550
watches. The Lord is near to those who

00:46:22.560 --> 00:46:25.030
weep in private. Every cry you've

00:46:25.040 --> 00:46:27.829
whispered, He's caught it. Every groan,

00:46:27.839 --> 00:46:30.630
He's recorded it. Every lonely night,

00:46:30.640 --> 00:46:33.829
you were never truly alone. The solitary

00:46:33.839 --> 00:46:37.910
intercessor is never invisible to God.

00:46:37.920 --> 00:46:39.910
I never saw most of the fruit I prayed

00:46:39.920 --> 00:46:41.910
for, but years later, the cities I

00:46:41.920 --> 00:46:44.069
groaned over would erupt in revival.

00:46:44.079 --> 00:46:46.390
What you birthed in solitude becomes

00:46:46.400 --> 00:46:49.030
fire that spreads publicly. Your secret

00:46:49.040 --> 00:46:50.950
place may look empty, but it is the

00:46:50.960 --> 00:46:55.910
epicenter of something holy.

00:46:55.920 --> 00:46:57.990
Lord, I say yes to the hidden path.

00:46:58.000 --> 00:46:59.990
Strengthen me in the lonely

00:47:00.000 --> 00:47:02.390
room. Remind me that I am not alone,

00:47:02.400 --> 00:47:04.150
that You are near to those who weep in

00:47:04.160 --> 00:47:06.790
secret. I choose the narrow way. I

00:47:06.800 --> 00:47:09.030
choose the silent room. I choose the

00:47:09.040 --> 00:47:11.589
weight that no one sees. Birth through

00:47:11.599 --> 00:47:17.990
me what will one day touch thousands.

00:47:18.000 --> 00:47:20.230
Revival is conceived in groaning. Before

00:47:20.240 --> 00:47:22.309
there's glory, there's groaning. You

00:47:22.319 --> 00:47:24.550
want to know where revival starts? It's

00:47:24.560 --> 00:47:26.630
not in the sanctuary, not in the sermon,

00:47:26.640 --> 00:47:29.750
but in the sound of groaning from a soul

00:47:29.760 --> 00:47:32.309
laid bare before God. Revival is

00:47:32.319 --> 00:47:34.790
conceived in the womb of agony. It is

00:47:34.800 --> 00:47:37.589
forged in the cries of the desperate. I

00:47:37.599 --> 00:47:39.430
never birthed anything with

00:47:39.440 --> 00:47:42.630
convenience. It was painful, raw, holy

00:47:42.640 --> 00:47:45.270
travail. That groan—it was

00:47:45.280 --> 00:47:47.349
heaven's signal that something divine

00:47:47.359 --> 00:47:50.230
was being formed. Groaning isn't a

00:47:50.240 --> 00:47:51.990
charismatic gimmick; it's spiritual

00:47:52.000 --> 00:47:54.870
labor. I groaned until my body shook,

00:47:54.880 --> 00:47:56.870
until my voice was gone, until the

00:47:56.880 --> 00:47:59.829
heavens broke open. That was when

00:47:59.839 --> 00:48:01.990
revival was conceived. I never saw

00:48:02.000 --> 00:48:04.710
revival fall until I first groaned for it.

00:48:04.720 --> 00:48:06.870
The church doesn't need more noise; it

00:48:06.880 --> 00:48:09.670
needs labor pains. You must be willing

00:48:09.680 --> 00:48:11.990
to carry what you cry for. Don't pray

00:48:12.000 --> 00:48:13.829
for revival if you're not willing to

00:48:13.839 --> 00:48:16.950
carry revival. It will cost you. It will

00:48:16.960 --> 00:48:18.870
crush you. It will strip you of comfort

00:48:18.880 --> 00:48:20.870
and convenience. But if you groan long

00:48:20.880 --> 00:48:22.950
enough, it will come. And when it does,

00:48:22.960 --> 00:48:28.390
it will change everything.

00:48:28.390 --> 00:48:28.400
It's

00:48:28.400 --> 00:48:29.109
good.

00:48:29.119 --> 00:48:31.430
Groaning in the Spirit,

00:48:31.440 --> 00:48:32.630
being led by the

00:48:32.640 --> 00:48:36.549
Spirit—it's

00:48:36.559 --> 00:48:38.309
a different level of prayer.

00:48:41.280 --> 00:48:45.670
That intimacy

00:48:45.680 --> 00:48:47.589
of going to the deeper levels with the

00:48:47.599 --> 00:48:51.589
Holy Spirit and flowing with Him

00:48:51.599 --> 00:48:55.190
in those rivers is what supernaturally...

00:48:55.200 --> 00:48:57.430
it's like the pool, you can feel it,

00:48:58.400 --> 00:49:00.549
going in with Him and flowing in that

00:49:00.559 --> 00:49:02.710
deeper level of prayer.

00:49:02.720 --> 00:49:04.470
I encourage every single one of you, if

00:49:04.480 --> 00:49:06.470
you're not baptized in the Holy Ghost,

00:49:06.480 --> 00:49:08.710
if you don't speak in other tongues, get

00:49:08.720 --> 00:49:11.589
the book Why Tongues by

00:49:11.589 --> 00:49:11.599
Kenneth

00:49:11.599 --> 00:49:13.270
E.

00:49:13.270 --> 00:49:13.280
Hagin.

00:49:13.280 --> 00:49:15.109
You can find it for free on

00:49:15.119 --> 00:49:17.270
YouTube; there's audio of

00:49:17.270 --> 00:49:17.280
people

00:49:17.280 --> 00:49:18.549
reading it to you,

00:49:18.800 --> 00:49:20.309
or if you Google it, I'm sure there's

00:49:20.319 --> 00:49:22.790
free PDFs.

00:49:22.800 --> 00:49:25.270
Just

00:49:25.280 --> 00:49:27.030
meditate on what Brother Hagin is

00:49:27.040 --> 00:49:29.109
teaching about tongues.

00:49:29.119 --> 00:49:31.750
Keep that down inside of you and stir

00:49:31.760 --> 00:49:33.910
it up.

00:49:33.920 --> 00:49:36.549
And the

00:49:36.559 --> 00:49:38.309
Holy Spirit is not going to come and just

00:49:38.319 --> 00:49:39.750
grab a hold of your tongue and wag it

00:49:39.760 --> 00:49:41.910
for you.

00:49:41.920 --> 00:49:44.630
You got to put your boat into motion.

00:49:44.640 --> 00:49:47.589
You've got to start making the sounds,

00:49:47.599 --> 00:49:49.750
and you'll feel out of your

00:49:49.760 --> 00:49:53.109
belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:49:53.119 --> 00:49:54.950
You'll feel it once you start

00:49:54.960 --> 00:49:57.349
getting in that flow, and you'll know

00:49:57.359 --> 00:49:58.870
that the Holy Spirit is praying

00:49:58.880 --> 00:49:59.990
for you. It's not just flesh. You go,

00:50:00.000 --> 00:50:02.069
"Well, is that me or is that the

00:50:02.079 --> 00:50:04.710
devil or

00:50:04.710 --> 00:50:04.720
whatever?"You

00:50:04.720 --> 00:50:06.309
start questioning things. You'll

00:50:06.319 --> 00:50:08.870
know. You can feel it.

00:50:10.480 --> 00:50:11.750
You'll feel it coming up out of your

00:50:11.760 --> 00:50:13.589
spirit, out of your flesh,

00:50:13.599 --> 00:50:15.190
out of your spirit coming

00:50:15.200 --> 00:50:16.710
out of your flesh.

00:50:16.720 --> 00:50:17.910
And it's not fleshly;

00:50:19.280 --> 00:50:21.349
you'll know. And I'm going to tell

00:50:21.359 --> 00:50:24.549
you the real Holy Ghost flow.

00:50:24.559 --> 00:50:26.470
There's many of you that don't know

00:50:26.480 --> 00:50:27.990
about it because it's not taught a lot

00:50:28.000 --> 00:50:31.190
in church. Acts chapter 2, going through

00:50:31.200 --> 00:50:33.990
when the

00:50:34.000 --> 00:50:35.670
Holy Spirit came on them in the upper

00:50:35.680 --> 00:50:39.670
room, the cloven tongues as a

00:50:39.680 --> 00:50:42.470
fire, and they all were

00:50:42.480 --> 00:50:43.910
looking at—they were drunk in the Holy

00:50:43.920 --> 00:50:45.430
Ghost and all the things that were

00:50:45.440 --> 00:50:47.990
happening up there. That same Holy

00:50:48.000 --> 00:50:50.630
Spirit that did it 2,000 years ago is

00:50:50.640 --> 00:50:53.349
still doing it today. The baptism of the

00:50:53.359 --> 00:50:56.230
Holy Spirit is for today. And there's

00:50:56.240 --> 00:50:57.750
many of you that have put a wall up to

00:50:57.760 --> 00:50:59.349
it because it sounds a little weird

00:50:59.359 --> 00:51:01.109
sometimes. You think, "Brandon, I asked so

00:51:01.119 --> 00:51:03.190
many questions."People ask me, "Brandon,

00:51:03.200 --> 00:51:05.430
what are you doing? What are you saying?

00:51:05.440 --> 00:51:07.270
What are you praying?"All the things

00:51:07.280 --> 00:51:09.190
that people are always so curious about

00:51:09.200 --> 00:51:10.549
because people aren't talking about

00:51:10.559 --> 00:51:14.150
it. But it's just me praying in tongues.

00:51:14.160 --> 00:51:15.990
Praying in the spirit. Praying in the

00:51:16.000 --> 00:51:18.549
spirit with a brand new tongue. Yielding

00:51:18.559 --> 00:51:21.270
to the Holy Spirit and letting him flow

00:51:21.280 --> 00:51:23.510
through me. And he'll do the same for

00:51:23.520 --> 00:51:26.470
you. I believe that every believer can

00:51:26.480 --> 00:51:29.190
pray in tongues. Get the book

00:51:29.200 --> 00:51:30.710
"Why tongues,"like I said, and just

00:51:30.720 --> 00:51:32.470
meditate on it and read those

00:51:32.480 --> 00:51:34.710
scriptures. Read it. Meditate on what

00:51:34.720 --> 00:51:36.470
brother Hagin's saying, and it will

00:51:36.480 --> 00:51:38.630
change you. And you know what? You

00:51:38.640 --> 00:51:41.430
say, "Lord, I..."You get quiet. "Lord, help

00:51:41.440 --> 00:51:43.829
me. I want to be baptized in the

00:51:43.839 --> 00:51:46.870
Holy Ghost. Help me to pray

00:51:46.880 --> 00:51:49.109
on another level.

00:51:49.119 --> 00:51:50.790
I don't want to just be praying in

00:51:50.800 --> 00:51:52.630
English. And I don't want to just be

00:51:52.630 --> 00:51:52.640
at

00:51:52.640 --> 00:51:55.109
this normal level,

00:51:55.119 --> 00:51:58.549
but teach me to pray.

00:51:58.559 --> 00:52:01.589
Teach me to pray on another

00:52:01.589 --> 00:52:01.599
level."And

00:52:01.599 --> 00:52:04.470
I believe the Holy Spirit will

00:52:04.480 --> 00:52:07.030
help you. He'll teach you all things.

00:52:07.040 --> 00:52:08.630
He'll lead you into all things.

00:52:08.640 --> 00:52:10.470
He'll make you come up higher in

00:52:10.480 --> 00:52:13.829
your prayer life with him.

00:52:13.839 --> 00:52:17.990
Visions and things add to

00:52:17.990 --> 00:52:18.000
it. The Lord's

00:52:18.000 --> 00:52:21.030
gifts are there for

00:52:21.040 --> 00:52:22.950
edifying the body, to show us how to pray

00:52:22.950 --> 00:52:22.960
and

00:52:22.960 --> 00:52:25.430
where to go in the spirit. And

00:52:25.440 --> 00:52:27.270
as far as what's coming and things

00:52:27.280 --> 00:52:29.750
like that, a watchman—not everybody's

00:52:29.760 --> 00:52:31.030
going to see in the spirit, not

00:52:31.040 --> 00:52:32.390
everybody's going to do things, but

00:52:32.400 --> 00:52:33.910
everybody has the ability to hear the

00:52:33.920 --> 00:52:35.990
Lord.

00:52:36.000 --> 00:52:38.390
Everybody has the ability to have a

00:52:38.400 --> 00:52:40.950
relationship with the Lord. He said, "My

00:52:40.960 --> 00:52:43.829
sheep will hear me and a stranger's

00:52:43.839 --> 00:52:46.309
voice they will not

00:52:46.309 --> 00:52:46.319
follow."So

00:52:46.319 --> 00:52:47.910
you say, "Well, I'm not baptized

00:52:47.910 --> 00:52:47.920
in

00:52:47.920 --> 00:52:49.030
the Holy Ghost. Does that mean I can't

00:52:49.040 --> 00:52:50.230
